tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE feedback (
  feedback_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  rating INT,
  comment TEXT,
  date_created TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE feedbacks (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    rating INT,
    comments TEXT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE ratings (
    rating_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT,
    customer_id INT,
    rating INT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
);
